snippet.title: Auto Chess trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
The makers of the original Auto Chess mod for DOTA 2 have teamed up with Epic Games to make an official Auto Chess game exclusive to the Epic Games Store.

Check out the full article here: https://www.pcgamer.com/the-dota-auto-chess-modders-are-making-a-version-exclusive-to-the-epic-games-store/
